Package: golden-rng
Version: 5.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: any
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.17), libssl3 | libssl1.1 (>= 1.1.0)
Maintainer: Golden RNG Team <surffero2077@proton.me>
Description: Golden RNG Enterprise - Cryptographic Random Number Generator
 A high-performance cryptographic random number generator (CSPRNG) implementing
 the AUR3ES algorithm with SHA-512 key derivation.
 .
 Features:
  - Cryptographically secure random number generation
  - Multi-platform support
  - SIMD optimized (SSE2, AVX2, AVX-512)
  - Multi-threaded parallel generation
  - Full NIST SP 800-22 statistical test suite
Homepage: https://github.com/phenixsam/aur3es

